## Exercise 1 - Solution

::: panel-tabset
### Code


```{.r .cell-code}
# Load necessary libraries
library(dplyr)

# Sample data frame with demographic data
set.seed(123)
data <- data.frame(
  id = 1:100,
  age = sample(18:80, 100, replace = TRUE),
  gender = sample(c("Male", "Female"), 100, replace = TRUE),
  treatment = sample(c("Treatment A", "Treatment B"), 100, replace = TRUE)
)

head(data)
```

