## Exercise 1 - Bonus Solution

Here is how to do it in {rtables} (for tabulation) and {tern} (for the summary functions):

::: panel-tabset
### Code


```{.r .cell-code}
library(rtables)
library(tern)

lyt <- basic_table() |> 
  split_cols_by("treatment") |> 
  analyze_vars(c("gender", "age"))

build_table(lyt, data)
```

